claim.claim-text:
50. A method comprising: 
presenting at least one customization option to a guest via a remote controller in communication with a server; 
receiving, at the server, at least one customization selection via the remote controller; 
providing the guest with a customization identifier corresponding to the customization selection via the remote controller; and 
configuring casino options, based on the customization selection, upon receipt of a customization request that includes the customization identifier from the guest via a check-in terminal.

53. A method comprising: 
receiving a preparation request from a user; 
associating the preparation request with a code; 
storing the code and preparation request; and 
fulfilling the preparation request upon receipt of the code from the user.

59. A method comprising: 
receiving first data from a user; 
establishing a gambling insurance policy for the user based upon the first data; 
receiving second data from at least one gaming device related to gaming of the user; 
determining whether the user has a valid gambling insurance claim based on the second data; and 
paying out on the claim if it is valid.
